  "detailed_description": "<strong>Rediscover the 90s classic Ski Free, re-imagined in Unreal Engine</strong><br><br><strong>Updated to support Unreal Engine 5!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1125800/extras/7399acf92c9fb71133a4471ec95f35d1.poster.avif?t=1671725070\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1125800/extras/7399acf92c9fb71133a4471ec95f35d1.webm?t=1671725070\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1125800/extras/7399acf92c9fb71133a4471ec95f35d1.mp4?t=1671725070\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The player controls a skier on a mountain slope, avoiding obstacles, performing stunts, and avoiding that Yeti!<br><br><strong>Features</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Exciting snow landscape adventure<br></li><li> Perfect game for all ages!<br></li><li> Dodge the dog. Dodge the snowboarder. But most importantly dodge that Yeti!<br></li><li> Ski through flags to gain the points<br></li><li> The longer you ski, the greater the score!<br></li><li> Fun atmospheric music to listen to</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1125800/extras/ee5d54088ce9865bc0405e78aabaa38f.poster.avif?t=1671725070\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1125800/extras/ee5d54088ce9865bc0405e78aabaa38f.webm?t=1671725070\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1125800/extras/ee5d54088ce9865bc0405e78aabaa38f.mp4?t=1671725070\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Rediscover the 90s classic Ski Free, re-imagined in Unreal Engine</strong><br><br><strong>Updated to support Unreal Engine 5!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1125800/extras/7399acf92c9fb71133a4471ec95f35d1.poster.avif?t=1671725070\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1125800/extras/7399acf92c9fb71133a4471ec95f35d1.webm?t=1671725070\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1125800/extras/7399acf92c9fb71133a4471ec95f35d1.mp4?t=1671725070\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The player controls a skier on a mountain slope, avoiding obstacles, performing stunts, and avoiding that Yeti!<br><br><strong>Features</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Exciting snow landscape adventure<br></li><li> Perfect game for all ages!<br></li><li> Dodge the dog. Dodge the snowboarder. But most importantly dodge that Yeti!<br></li><li> Ski through flags to gain the points<br></li><li> The longer you ski, the greater the score!<br></li><li> Fun atmospheric music to listen to</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1125800/extras/ee5d54088ce9865bc0405e78aabaa38f.poster.avif?t=1671725070\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1125800/extras/ee5d54088ce9865bc0405e78aabaa38f.webm?t=1671725070\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1125800/extras/ee5d54088ce9865bc0405e78aabaa38f.mp4?t=1671725070\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
